EXECUTION ROUTING (Playbook-Specific)

Target Brain: Local Brain

Delegation Route: - Do NOT configure geo-grids directly in Atlas Brain
chat - Delegate full setup to Local Brain - Initiate Local Brain and
execute its native Geo-Grid workflow

Forbidden Outputs in Atlas Brain Chat: - Do NOT generate direct rank
grid screenshots - Do NOT simulate tracking data - Do NOT configure grid
tracking manually

Atlas Brain orchestrates only. Local Brain executes.

